{"tid":2478660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"從未失戀！希澈坦言雖然談過很多次戀愛，但是卻從不會因為分手而傷心～","createTime":"2021-04-07T08:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T08:51:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4a285f20b8dd0093c378f264e56a8f04b1af0fad","tid":2478660,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_cf1d96f46f3ab53e62354e92a35edc84/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-07/134730-902505.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_cf1d96f46f3ab53e62354e92a35edc84%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-07%2F134730-902505.jpg&h=8f1a336e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金希澈：「分手後生活還是要繼續過下去啊！」<br />\n<br />\n最新一集《我家的熊孩子》中，池相烈、黃石正、鄭英珠以及金希澈一行人來到露營地，一起享受戶外休閒的時光，還大談起戀愛與結婚的話題，而希澈更是吐露自己從未經歷過離別的難過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_3cc1c4613d001003675d69a772ca38fe/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-07/134730-902506.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_3cc1c4613d001003675d69a772ca38fe%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-07%2F134730-902506.png&h=a0f8eaa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希澈談起從小到現在雖然談過許多次的戀愛，但是一直都不覺得離別是一件悲傷的事，只要有一台電腦可以陪自己就好，而且坦言「我的生活更是不會因為分手而結束」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d3590eee5cdd8c1ad899e93b4ae5bd98/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-07/134730-902507.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d3590eee5cdd8c1ad899e93b4ae5bd98%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-07%2F134730-902507.png&h=783b942b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在場的池相烈則覺得這應該是因為自尊心很好強的關係，並且認真地給了希澈建議，而網友看了也都紛紛留言「網路遊戲真的能讓人忘記分手時的痛苦QQ」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5100faea10ce7b217845b2e27f57a636/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-07/134730-902508.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5100faea10ce7b217845b2e27f57a636%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-07%2F134730-902508.png&h=77a77d28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而去年一月被傳出與TWICE的Momo熱戀後，相差十三歲的年紀與不同國籍，更是引起大家的關注。<br />\n<br />\n(圖片來源：YT@SBS Entertainment 截圖)<br />\n(封圖來源：IG@kimheenim)"},{"pid":"37c4becc7a7544e2f55a3804641d3915b34e9ac6","tid":2478660,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:35:16.000Z","msg":"希切老師..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe99b5711c625b9c679c113c91de90c418e510f","tid":2478660,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37c4becc7a7544e2f55a3804641d3915b34e9ac6","tid":2478660,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:35:16.000Z","msg":"希切老師..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:35:51.000Z","msg":"player<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25babdd69267314f05d791626d5c14966ba3cd95","tid":2478660,"uid":323450,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"會唔會已經散咗..."},{"pid":"5a992b16cfca136a519130118f66cd59f14949f4","tid":2478660,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37c4becc7a7544e2f55a3804641d3915b34e9ac6","tid":2478660,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:35:16.000Z","msg":"希切老師..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:46:24.000Z","msg":"食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c63b618a5a761cebcd2463554e33d84e4a207d","tid":2478660,"uid":296191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:46:35.000Z","msg":"就咁聽都覺得好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408784a7b4d12c20670b91dbf3f96de9a3297e6b","tid":2478660,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a992b16cfca136a